#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.metrics.precision_score.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.metrics.precision\\_score"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:1 of
msgid "Compute the precision"
msgstr "计算精确率"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:3 of
msgid ""
"The precision is the ratio ``tp / (tp + fp)`` where ``tp`` is the number "
"of true positives and ``fp`` the number of false positives. The precision"
" is intuitively the ability of the classifier not to label as positive a "
"sample that is negative."
msgstr ""
"精确率是 ``tp / (tp + fp)`` 的比率，其中 ``tp`` 是真正例的数量，``fp`` 是"
"假正例的数量。直观地讲，精确率是分类器不将负样本标记为正样本的能力。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:8 of
msgid "The best value is 1 and the worst value is 0."
msgstr "最佳值是 1，最差值是 0。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:10 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <precision_recall_f_measure_metrics>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:12 of
msgid "Ground truth (correct) target values."
msgstr "真实（正确）的目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:14 of
msgid "Estimated targets as returned by a classifier."
msgstr "由分类器返回的预测目标值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:16 of
msgid ""
"The set of labels to include when ``average != 'binary'``, and their "
"order if ``average is None``. Labels present in the data can be excluded,"
" for example to calculate a multiclass average ignoring a majority "
"negative class, while labels not present in the data will result in 0 "
"components in a macro average. For multilabel targets, labels are column "
"indices. By default, all labels in ``y_true`` and ``y_pred`` are used in "
"sorted order."
msgstr ""
"当 ``average != 'binary'`` 时要包含的标签集合，以及当 ``average is None``"
" 时这些标签的顺序。数据中存在的标签可以被排除，例如计算多类平均值时忽略"
"多数负类；而数据中不存在的标签在宏平均中会导致 0 分量。对于多标签目标，"
"标签是列索引。默认情况下，``y_true`` 和 ``y_pred`` 中的所有标签都按排序"
"顺序使用。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:24 of
msgid ""
"The class to report if ``average='binary'`` and the data is binary. If "
"the data are multiclass or multilabel, this will be ignored; setting "
"``labels=[pos_label]`` and ``average != 'binary'`` will report scores for"
" that label only."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``average='binary'`` 且数据是二分类的，则报告此类别。如果数据是多类"
"或多标签的，则此参数将被忽略；设置 ``labels=[pos_label]`` 且 ``average !="
" 'binary'`` 将仅报告该标签的得分。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:29 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This parameter is required for multiclass/multilabel targets. If "
"``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:  ``'binary'``:"
"     Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``.     "
"This is applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary. "
"``'micro'``:     Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true "
"positives,     false negatives and false positives. ``'macro'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted     mean.  "
"This does not take label imbalance into account. ``'weighted'``:     "
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted     by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This     alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an     F-score "
"that is not between precision and recall. ``'samples'``:     Calculate "
"metrics for each instance, and find their average (only     meaningful "
"for multilabel classification where this differs from     "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""
"对于多类/多标签目标，此参数是必需的。如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类别的"
"得分。否则，此参数决定对数据执行的平均类型：``'binary'``：仅报告由 ``pos_"
"label`` 指定的类别的结果。这仅适用于目标（``y_{true,pred}``）为二分类的"
"情况。``'micro'``：通过计算总的真正例、假负例和假正例来全局计算指标。``'"
"macro'``：为每个标签计算指标，并计算它们的未加权平均值。这不考虑标签不"
"平衡。``'weighted'``：为每个标签计算指标，并根据支持度（每个标签的真实"
"实例数）计算它们的加权平均值。这会调整 'macro' 以考虑标签不平衡；可能导致"
" F-score 不在精确率和召回率之间。``'samples'``：为每个实例计算指标，并"
"计算它们的平均值（仅对与 :func:`accuracy_score` 不同的多标签分类有意义）"
"。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:29 of
msgid ""
"This parameter is required for multiclass/multilabel targets. If "
"``None``, the scores for each class are returned. Otherwise, this "
"determines the type of averaging performed on the data:"
msgstr ""
"此参数对于多类/多标签目标是必需的。如果为 ``None``，则返回每个类的分数。"
"否则，这确定对数据执行的平均类型："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:33 of
msgid "``'binary'``:"
msgstr "``'binary'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:34 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Only report results for the class specified by ``pos_label``. This is "
"applicable only if targets (``y_{true,pred}``) are binary."
msgstr ""
"仅报告 ``pos_label`` 指定的类的结果。这仅适用于目标（``y_{true,pred}``）"
"为二进制的情况。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:36 of
msgid "``'micro'``:"
msgstr "``'micro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:37 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics globally by counting the total true positives, false "
"negatives and false positives."
msgstr "通过计算总的真正例、假反例和假正例来全局计算指标。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:39 of
msgid "``'macro'``:"
msgstr "``'macro'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:40 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their unweighted mean.  This "
"does not take label imbalance into account."
msgstr "计算每个标签的指标，并找到它们的未加权平均值。这不考虑标签不平衡。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:42 of
msgid "``'weighted'``:"
msgstr "``'weighted'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:43 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each label, and find their average weighted by "
"support (the number of true instances for each label). This alters "
"'macro' to account for label imbalance; it can result in an F-score that "
"is not between precision and recall."
msgstr ""
"计算每个标签的指标，并根据支持度（每个标签的真实实例数）计算加权平均值。"
"这会修改 'macro' 以考虑标签不平衡；可能导致 F 分数不在精确率和召回率之间"
"。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:47 of
msgid "``'samples'``:"
msgstr "``'samples'``："

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:48 of
msgid ""
"Calculate metrics for each instance, and find their average (only "
"meaningful for multilabel classification where this differs from "
":func:`accuracy_score`)."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:52 of
msgid "Sample weights."
msgstr "样本权重。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:54 of
msgid ""
"Sets the value to return when there is a zero division. If set to "
"\"warn\", this acts as 0, but warnings are also raised."
msgstr ""
"设置当出现零除时返回的值。如果设置为 \"warn\"，则其作用为 0，但也会引发"
"警告。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:58 of
msgid ""
"**precision** -- Precision of the positive class in binary classification"
" or weighted average of the precision of each class for the multiclass "
"task."
msgstr ""
"**precision** -- 二分类中正类的精确率，或多类任务中各类别精确率的加权"
"平均值。"

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:62 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`precision_recall_fscore_support`, "
":py:obj:`multilabel_confusion_matrix`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:65 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:84 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.precision_score:85 of
msgid ""
"When ``true positive + false positive == 0``, precision returns 0 and "
"raises ``UndefinedMetricWarning``. This behavior can be modified with "
"``zero_division``."
msgstr ""
"当 ``true positive + false positive == 0`` 时，precision 返回 0 并引发 ``"
"UndefinedMetricWarning``。此行为可以通过 ``zero_division`` 进行修改。"

